    "Turning about to face the empty lane in the way I had just come, I stop where I stand to fix my tights again, sticking my hands under my skirt up to pinch and dig at the tght fabric to sort it out."
    g1 "Dear me, Vincenza, and the in the sight of the Virgin Mary too."
    g2 "Come now, Vittoria, the Virgin Mary {b}always{/b} watches over us."
    C "(Who is that?)"
    "From behind, unexpectedly, come a pair of voices and a titter of laughter against the quiet of the evening dust of snowfall."
    "Before my mind can process it any further, a sudden weight presses around the back of my neck and upon my shoulders."
    O "The proper young ladies of the academy do such things in the confines of their own rooms."
    "The second girl's voice is close, close enough for me to feel the warmth of her breath on the left side of my face."
    "Flipping my head suddenly to the side, I catch sight of the face of the girl in question. She wears a soft grin upon a graceful pale face, set below sharp but cheerful eyes."
    "From her head falls hair of fine silver across her face, gathering neatly down her back."
    H "Maybe she isn't a proper young lady at all?"
    "A soft touch against the small of my back announces the arrival of the first girl, and it remains as she swoops close across my other side in a flutter of golden curls more toward my front."
    "When my head flips back the other way, I find that this girl shares similar features to the first, her flowing golden tresses notwithstanding."
    "The first thought through my brain is that they must be sisters, with a common foreign accent adding to the similarity."
    C "(What... the hell is happening?)"
    "The golden-haired girl draws close to my face, reaching a hand toward my chin to guide my face in momentary inspection."
    H "A young lady, for sure, but the question of her {b}propriety{/b} remains."
    "So goes my second thought. Frozen in place with confusion, the pair continue on their back and forth with barely an ackowledgement of me besides their hands {b}all over{/b} my body."
    O "You've kept us waiting, Clover. We have a very important meeting to attend."
    "With her right arm still heavy around my shoulders, her left heedlessly picks at the leftmost strap of my jumper skirt, following it slowly all the way up my chest."
    C "...My bus was late. H-Hey, what are you—!"
    "I might have totally forgotten that I had my skirt pulled up to pick at my tights when I suddenly froze in place, but the girl on my right certainly hasn't."
    "The hand of hers which isn't on my small of my back drop from my chin and brushes against the hand I was using to fix my tights, only to go further still, picking up where I had left off."
    H "Oh my, and with your uniform so disarrayed. Please allow me to assist. You want to make a good first impression for your Vertu, is that right?"
    "She pulls at the tights bunching around my knees and slides the palm of her hand up my leg with it, smoothing the thin material across my thighs."
    "My body tingles with the smoothness of her touch, however stiff I am with the shock and confusion of someone acting so out of ordinary convention."
    O "The poor little thing's frozen solid. Can we not keep her just a little longer, Vittoria?"
    "The strap of my jumper is released from the second girl's fingers, but rather than remove them, she goes yet further to lay her hand across my chest."
    "Her fingers tease their tips slowly between the buttons of my blouse, catching just slightly on each as she trails her way up to straighten the pink necktie at the very top."
    H "We were only asked to deliver her room key, Vincenza, and we are late ourselves as you rightly pointed out."
    "The first girl's palm glides well higher than it has any right to up the inside of my thigh, flattening out with the tights out around my hip."
    O "Pity..."
    "Distracted and slowed from logical thought by the strange caresses all over my body, it's only then that I come to the heart of the matter."
    C "W-Wait, room key?"
    "With a soft giggle, the first girl's fingers clip against my stomach where the white tights meet their end, followed by the hard, cold touch of something entirely inhuman against my bare skin."
    C "H-Hyah!"
    "I quiver instinctively against the cold metal wedged between my skin and my tights and break the stupor the mysterious pair of girls had put me in."
    "The heavy duffel strap still slung over my shoulder finally drops off as I shake about trying to fish out the object from inside my tights."
    "I hold the offending item up before my face as I do, finding a plastic id card with my face on it staring back, a metal carabiner attached to it."
    C "Y-You—!"
    "For a moment I am about to let loose on the two girls beside me, only to find that they're no longer clinging to me at all, which makes sense in how easily I was able to retrieve the key."
    "Whipping around, I find them already strolling arm-in-arm back toward the academy."
    H "Le abbiamo sicuramente piegato gli spaghetti."
    O "Certamente."
    "Now that my brain has caught up, I'm half confused and half {b}fuming{/b}. I can feel the heat rising in my cheeks, and the extra puffy breaths of air emerging from my lungs."
    "But rather than chase after them, now a fair distance away, I resign myself to heaving my duffel back over my shoulder and finally read the keycard in my hand."
    C "(Macaron Dormitory, Room 28)"
    scene bg transition with fade
    pause 1.0
    jump vertu

